Is it  possible to remove outer rear axle bearings without the use of special 
 
tool (puller) VW 241A?


Hi Phil,
Sure!  We just put a piece of wood over the axle and tap with a  hammer 
against the wood.  If that does not work you can make a puller  by checking out the 
Idiot's Manual.
